&lt;p&gt;With our unique access to the largest opted-in network of HCPs, their insights, and clinical expertise, we are the leading provider of AI technology and real-time channels that life science companies need to deliver clear, reliable, and evidence-based resources directly into the hands of HCPs. Guided by a council of 2000+ trusted HCP advisors, we ensure every interaction is clinically meaningful, ethically grounded and leads to better patient care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Summary:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a commercial &lt;strong&gt;Data Analyst&lt;/strong&gt; at Impiricus, you will play a vital role in driving data-informed decision-making across our commercial operations. You will be responsible for analyzing campaign performance, supporting client-facing teams with actionable insights. This position combines analytical expertise with business acumen to deliver valuable insights that enhance our client relationships and drive business growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Campaign Performance Analysis &amp;amp; Insights&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze campaign performance to identify trends, measure effectiveness, and deliver actionable recommendations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate complex data into clear business narratives that support commercial strategy and client success.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop dashboards and recurring reports to monitor key performance metrics and drive data-informed decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Commercial Analytics&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Client Services and Sales to provide analytical support for client conversations, quarterly business reviews (QBRs), and commercial initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze cross-campaign and cross-brand performance to uncover insights that inform business development and growth strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage internal and external data sources to generate recommendations that improve commercial outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Management &amp;amp; Reporting&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build, validate, and optimize target lists while ensuring data quality and reporting accuracy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create impactful visualizations and reports using business intelligence tools for technical and non-technical stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify opportunities to improve reporting processes through automation, AI-enabled tools, and continuous process improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree, STEM field preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1–3 years of experience in data analytics, business analytics, marketing analytics, decision science, or a related analytical role in a consulting or agency setting.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid experience using data visualization tools such as Sigma, Tableau, Power BI, or similar BI platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong SQL skills, including the ability to understand and interpret complex queries, joins, and analytical outputs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with Excel or Google Sheets for data analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with AI-assisted analytics, workflow automation, or modern productivity tools that enhance reporting and data analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical and problem-solving skills with exceptional attention to detail.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills with the ability to translate data into actionable business insights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to manage competing priorities while collaborating effectively with cross-functional teams and stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Healthcare, health-tech, or pharmaceutical experience preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The base salary range for this role is&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;$85,000 - $95,000.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Where you land within the range will reflect your skills, experience, and location, while keeping team parity in mind and leaving room for future growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
